CREATE TABLE election_results (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR,
    party_affiliation VARCHAR,
    votes_received INT
);

CREATE TABLE election_results (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(255),
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
    votes_received INT
);

CREATE TABLE voter_demographics (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    region VARCHAR(50),
    voting_district INT
);

CREATE TABLE election_results (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    election_type VARCHAR(50),
    winning_party VARCHAR(50),
    voter_turnout INT
);

CREATE TABLE candidate_data (
    candidate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(100),
    candidate_party VARCHAR(50),
    candidate_age INT,
    candidate_gender CHAR(1)
);

CREATE TABLE voter_demographics (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_age INT,
    voter_gender CHAR(1),
    voter_location VARCHAR(100),
    voter_party_preference VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE election_participants (
    election_id INT,
    party_id INT,
    district_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (election_id) REFERENCES election_results(election_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (party_id) REFERENCES political_parties(party_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (district_id) REFERENCES voting_districts(district_id)
);

CREATE TABLE election_results (
    election_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_year INT,
    candidate_name VARCHAR(50),
    party_affiliation VARCHAR(50),
    total_votes INT
);

CREATE TABLE election_votes (
    vote_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    election_id INT,
    voter_id INT,
    candidate_id INT,
    vote_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
